# Width guideline

- Use the Tailwind token `max-w-card` for all central cards on desktop.
- Current desktop width is 820px (`max-w-card`). Adjust this token for global width changes.
- Components should center with `mx-auto` and respect container padding (`px-6` and max page width `max-w-[1200px]`).

Usage example:

```tsx
<div className="mx-auto w-full max-w-card">...</div>
```
